********************Interview question*********************************

1)Diffrence between  first() and get()

first() Method:   Retrieves a single record from the database.
get() Method:     Retrieves a collection of records from the database.

2)Difference between get() and all()
all()    is a convenient shortcut for fetching all records of a model when no specific filtering or ordering is required beforehand.
get()    is used when you need to build a more complex query with conditions, ordering, or specific column selections before retrieving the results.

