Que & jobs
A job is a specific task to be executed, like sending an email,
Queue is a waiting list that holds these jobs until a worker is available to process them.


 




A SQL engine, also known as a SQL database engine or database engine, is the core software component within a Database Management System (DBMS) responsible for processing and managing data in a relational database.

How to prevent sql injection

a)Web Application Firewalls
b)Keep Software Up to Date
c)Use Stored Procedures -> A stored procedure is a precompiled set of SQL statements that are stored and executed on the database server.
d)Use Prepared Statements




In PHP, we have the following loop types:

while - loops through a block of code as long as the specified condition is true
do...while - loops through a block of code once, and then repeats the loop as long as the specified condition is true
for - loops through a block of code a specified number of times
foreach - loops through a block of code for each element in an array




Cookies are client-side files that are stored on a local computer.
Sessions are server-side files  that are stored on server.







